about.summary: This is a python module provide a wrapper of terraform command line tool

name: python-terraform
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "python-terraform" %}
{% set version = "0.10.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/beelit94/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 81732172b49460b4b79253b7b5dcf6dfdf6a4fe088edf4ae4b909c165d4da871

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - python_terraform

about:
  home: https://github.com/beelit94/python-terraform
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: This is a python module provide a wrapper of terraform command line tool
  dev_url: https://github.com/beelit94/python-terraform

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - agcopenhaver
    - oblute
    - rluria14
